ation%20on%20AI%20safety%20to%20help%20build%20an%20international%20%E2%80%9Cgovernance%20framework.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech%20leaders%20praise%20AI%20summit%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fakademie.dw.com%2Fen%2Fan-opportunity-and-a-threat-the-race-for-ai%2Fa-66683778%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22External%20link%20%E2%80%94%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20potential%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0raises%20many%20hopes%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcancer-prevention-would-you-want-ai-to-predict-your-fate%2Fa-66958621%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20for%20medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20development%20is%20seen%20as%20largely%20unchecked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20tech%20experts%20and%20political%20leaders%20have%20warned%20that%20the%20accelerated%20development%20of%20AI%20poses%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20the%20world%20if%20not%20regulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20tech%20attendees%20were%C2%A0Sam%20Altman%2C%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20the%20firm%20behind%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Felon-musk%2Ft-63587027%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%20and%20owner%20of%20social%20media%20company%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fx-formerly-known-as-twitter%2Ft-38240794%5C%22%3EX%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0who%20described%20the%20event%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctimely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%E2%80%99re%20really%20aiming%20for%20here%20is%20to%20establish%20a%20framework%20for%20insight%20so%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20at%20least%20a%20third-party%20referee%2C%20an%20independent%20referee%2C%20that%20can%20observe%20what%20leading%20AI%20companies%20are%20doing%20and%20at%20least%20sound%20the%20alarm%20if%20they%20have%20concerns%2C%E2%80%9D%20Musk%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20existential%20risks%20that%20we%20face%20and%20it%20is%20potentially%20the%20most%20pressing%20one%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20timescale%20and%20rate%20of%20advancement%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20summit%20is%20timely%2C%20and%20I%20applaud%20the%20prime%20minister%20for%20holding%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Carticle%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20seeks%20policy%20lead%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20Commerce%20Gina%20Raimondo%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20US%20will%20launch%20an%20AI%20safety%20institute%20to%20evaluate%20known%20and%20emerging%20risks%20of%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cfrontier%E2%80%9D%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20calling%20on%20many%20of%20you%20in%20the%20audience%20who%20are%20in%20academia%20and%20industry%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20consortium%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20to%20the%20AI%20Safety%20Summit%20in%20Britain.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20alone%2C%20the%20private%20sector%20must%20step%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaimondo%20added%20that%20she%20would%20also%20commit%20to%20the%20US%20institute%20establishing%20a%20formal%20partnership%20with%20the%20UK%20Safety%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20due%20to%20attend%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20event%20but%20caused%20some%20surprise%20among%20UK%20officials%20by%20giving%20a%20speech%20on%20AI%20at%20the%20US%20Embassy%20in%20London%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20holding%20some%20meetings%20with%20attendees%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20leave%20early.%20Her%20speech%20made%20only%20a%20passing%20reference%20to%20the%20Bletchley%20Park%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing%20that%20the%20US%20has%20announced%20a%20policy%20blitz%20to%20coincide%20with%20the%20summit%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20source%20from%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20technology%20department%20told%20Reuters%20news%20agency.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20obviously%20prefer%20it%20if%20guests%20didn%E2%80%99t%20leave%20early.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjoe-biden%2Ft-55668302%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0signed%20an%20AI%20executive%20order%20requiring%20developers%20of%20AI%20systems%20that%20pose%20risks%20to%20US%20national%20security%2C%20the%20economy%2C%20public%20health%20or%20safety%2C%20to%20share%20the%20results%20of%20safety%20tests%20with%20the%20US%20government%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Defense%20Production%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20used%20the%20event%20to%20announce%20its%20plan%20to%20invest%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E300%20million%20(%24364%20million)%20in%20AI%20supercomputing%2C%20boosting%20funding%20from%20the%20previously%20announced%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E100%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Farticle%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fai-summit-in-uk-seeks-global-consensus-on-mitigating-risk%2Fa-67279381%5C%22%3Estory%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698925925000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02120652%2FAI-Safety-Summit-1-e1698907074576.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fai-summit-in-uk-seeks-global-consensus-on-mitigating-risk%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20world's%20first%20artifi