6000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104913618%2Cimgsize-571074.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fvladimir-putin-revokes-russias-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty%2Farticleshow%2F104913528.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104913528.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPresident%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20signed%20a%20bill%20to%20revoke%20Russia's%20ratification%20of%20the%20Comprehensive%20Nuclear%20Test%20Ban%20Treaty%20(CTBT)%2C%20citing%20the%20need%20to%20establish%20parity%20with%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20CTBT%2C%20adopted%20in%201996%2C%20bans%20nuclear%20explosions%20globally%20but%20has%20not%20been%20fully%20implemented.%20Russia's%20move%20has%20raised%20concerns%20that%20it%20may%20resume%20nuclear%20tests%20to%20deter%20Western%20military%20support%20for%20Ukraine.%20However%2C%20Russian%20Deputy%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Ryabkov%20stated%20that%20Moscow%20will%20only%20resume%20tests%20if%20the%20US%20does%20so%20first.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fvladimir-putin-revokes-russias-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty%2Farticleshow%2F104913528.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fvladimir-putin-revokes-russias-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty%2Famp_articleshow%2F104913528.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fvladimir-putin-revokes-russias-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty%2Famp_articleshow%2F104913528.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What's%20Holding%20Back%20the%20Military's%20Plan%20to%20Institute%20Integrated%20Theatre%20Commands%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02135719%2FF92K5a0XsAAs1Bq.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Progress%20in%20instituting%20Integrated%20Theatre%20Commands%20(ITC)%20by%20the%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20(CDS)%20General%20Anil%20Chauhan%2C%20to%20augment%20inter-service%20synergy%2C%20is%20reportedly%20stalled%2C%20principally%20over%20the%20knotty%20and%20lingering%20issue%20surrounding%20the%20overall%20operational%20control%20of%20the%20proposed%20formations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20recent%20media%20reports%2C%20citing%20official%20sources%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Military%20Affairs%20(DMA)%20which%20General%20Chauhan%20heads%2C%20is%20also%20%E2%80%98re-evaluating%E2%80%99%20its%20earlier%20plans%20of%20creating%20three%20ITCs%20%E2%80%93%20one%20each%20for%20the%20northern%20and%20western%20borders%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20an%20overarching%20maritime%2Fpeninsular%20command-and%20opting%20for%20%E2%80%98additional%20others%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20latter%20provision%20is%20reportedly%20under%20consideration%2C%20primarily%20to%20%E2%80%98accommodate%20service%20interests%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20euphemism%20for%20senior%20service%20officers%20retaining%20their%20ranks%2C%20multiple%20privileges%20and%20perquisites%20which%2C%20other%20than%20existing%20exaggerated%20pomp%20and%20majesty%2C%20included%20exclusive%20use%20of%20aircraft%20and%20rotary%20assets%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20cross-section%20of%20senior%20military%20veterans%20maintain%20that%20determining%20the%20overarching%20operational%20head%20of%20the%20ITCs%20remains%20the%20CDS%E2%80%99s%20principal%20challenge%2C%20before%20formally%20forwarding%20the%20architecture%20of%20these%20joint%20battle%20groups%20to%20the%20government%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20earlier%20for%20completion%20by%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20proposed%20structure%20of%20the%20theatre%20commands%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20finalised%2C%20there%20are%20some%20important%20issues%20where%20greater%20deliberation%20is%20required%2C%E2%80%9D%20declared%20military%20analyst%2C%20retired%20Lieutenant%20General%20H.S.%20Hooda%20in%20an%20analysis%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Policy%20Group%20think%20tank%20in%20August.%20The%20issue%20of%20how%20the%20command%20and%20control%20over%20the%20theatre%20commands%20will%20be%20exercised%20remains%20unclear%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20veterans%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20named%2C%20said%20that%20this%20%E2%80%98ticklish%E2%80%99%20issue%20of%20operational%20control%20over%20the%20ITCs%20was%20posing%20%E2%80%98grave%20problems%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20it%20was%20collectively%20%E2%80%98hobbled%E2%80%99%20by%20hierarchical%20inter%20and%20intra-service%20rivalries%2C%20conflicts%20of%20interest%20and%20personal%20ambitions.%20%E2%80%9CCompeting%20interests%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20resolve%20this%20critical%20concern%20swiftly%2C%E2%80%9D%20admitted%20a%20retired%20three-star%20Indian%20Navy%20(IN)%20officer%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%20It%20requires%20deftness%20and%20all-round%20placate-ability%20within%20the%20military%20to%20be%20agreeably%20resolved%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatters%20at%20the%20outset%20had%20been%20complicated%20by%20dealing%20with%20the%20CDS%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20post%E2%80%99s%20founding%20charter%20in%20December%202019%2C%20out%20of%20this%20operational%20equation%2C%20despite%20him%20being%20India%E2%80%99s%20senior-most%20soldier.%20Under%20his%20terms%20of%20employment%2C%20the%20CDS%20is%20denied%20any%20military%20command%2C%20including%20over%20the%20three%20Service%20Chiefs%2C%20and%20his%20remit%2C%20amongst%20a%20host%20of%20myriad%20other%20responsibilities%2C%20including%20prioritising%20materiel%20procurements%20and%20force%20modernisation%20is%2C%20as%20the%20sole%20provider%20of%20%E2%80%98impartial%20(military)%20advice%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20political%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22171955%2FF8OlZAaXEAAeXHw.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22171955%2FF8OlZAaXEAAeXHw.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22171955%2FF8OlZAaXEAAeXHw-300x191.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22171955%2FF8OlZAaXEAAeXHw-1024x653.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681288%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22765%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20with%20Army%2C%20BRO%20and%20ITBP%20personnel.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMedia%20reports%20also%20indicated%20that%20the%20role%20of%20the%20three%20four-star%20single%20service%20chiefs%20in%20the%20re-organised%20ITC%20milieu%2C%20which%20had%20earlier%20been%20envisaged%20as%20one%20merely%20encompassing%20recruiting%20and%20training%20manpower%20and%20logistically%20supporting%20it%2C%20too%20was%20being%20re-assessed.%20This%20review%2C%20prompted%20no%20doubt%20by%20the%20individual%20chiefs%20themselves%2C%20miffed%20at%20being%20sidelined%20to%20a%20secondary%20role%20in%20the%20overhauled%20higher%20defence%20management%20setting%2C%20supposedly%20aims%20at%20providing%20them%20with%20some%20%E2%80%98compensatory%E2%80%99%20operational%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20veterans%20argued%20that%20this%20would%20only%20further%20complicate%20the%20CDS%E2%80%99s%20task%20in%20finalising%20the%20ITCs%2C%20as%20conferring%20operational%20responsibilities%20upon%20these%20three%20service%20chiefs%20of%20staff%20in%20an%20exclusively%20multi-service%20environment%2C%20could%20end%20up%20not%20only%20impinging%20upon%20but%20also%20clashing%20with%20the%20battlefield%20authority%20of%20theatre%20commanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlongside%2C%20the%20earlier%20proposal%20of%20having%20four-star%20ITC%20commanders%20%E2%80%93%20on%20par%20with%20the%20service%20chiefs%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20shelved%2C%20as%20it%20was%20felt%20that%20such%20a%20move%20would%2C%20by%20default%2C%20have%20meant%20elevating%20the%20CDS%20to%20five-star%20or%20field%20marshal%20status.%20For%20now%2C%20however%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20ITC%20commanders%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20three-star%20officers%2C%20but%20independent%20%E2%80%93%20and%20yet%20not%20independent%20%E2%80%93%20of%20their%20senior%20in%20rank%2C%20four-star%20service%20chief%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVarious%20ITC%20models%20have%20been%20under%20consideration%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%3B%20but%20amazingly%20none%20had%20been%20finalised%20to%20meet%20the%202022%20deadline%20imposed%20on%20the%20first%20CDS%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20who%20died%20in%20a%20helicopter%20accident%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20December%202021.%20According%20to%20defence%20analyst%20Brigadier%20Rahul%20Bhonsle%20of%20the%20Security%20Risks%20Asia%20consultancy%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20all%20endeavours%20so%20far%20to%20formulate%20ITCs%20were%20an%20exercise%20in%20%E2%80%98reinventing%20the%20wheel%E2%80%99%2C%20leading%20only%20to%20recurring%20delays.%20Resistance%20from%20the%20services%20in%20this%20regard%20was%20also%20obvious%20in%20confirming%20the%20ITC%E2%80%99s%20unitary%20operational%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20parliament%20passed%20the%20Enabling%20Inter-Services%20Organisation%20(Command%2C%20Control%20%26amp%3B%20Discipline)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20provided%20inter-services%20commanders%20with%20disciplinary%20and%20administrative%20powers%20over%20multi-service%20personnel%20serving%20under%20them.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20had%20smoothed%20the%20way%20for%20the%20DMA%20to%20conclude%20its%20task%20of%20formulating%20ITCs%20in%20their%20entirety%20which%2C%20so%20far%2C%20it%20has%20failed%20to%20vindicate.%20This%20Bill%20also%20empowers%20the%20government%20to%20create%20additional%20organisations%20as%20required%2C%20thereby%20providing%20the%20DMA%20a%20clean%20slate%20to%20operationally%20structure%20the%20ITCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20veterans%20and%20analysts%20agreed%20that%20the%20projected%20ITC%20formations%20were%20%E2%80%98riddled%20with%20confusion%20and%20contradictions%E2%80%99%20at%20multiple%20levels%2C%20indicating%20that%20such%20a%20major%20transformation%20guaranteed%20to%20completely%20alter%20the%20Indian%20military%E2%80%99s%20overall%20composition%20forever%2C%20had%20entailed%20little%20or%20no%20credible%20planning.%20This%20was%20despite%20the%20creation%20of%20two%20multi-service%20organisations%20in%202001%20and%202007%20for%20the%20specific%20purpose%20of%20fostering%20%E2%80%98jointness%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20three%20armed%20forces%20once%20a%20CDS%20was%20appointed%2C%20which%20was%20in%20January%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20such%20recommendatory%20body%20was%20the%20Headquarters%20Integrated%20Defence%20Staff%20or%20HQ%20IDS%2C%20created%20in%20October%202001%2C%20following%20the%20recommendations%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Group%20of%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20after%20the%201999%20Kargil%20war%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20evolving%20the%20blueprint%20for%20tri-service%20cooperation%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20reforming%20numerous%20other%20inherent%20shortcomings%20to%20enhance%20operational%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20the%20IDS%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20two%20tri-service%20commands%20of%20which%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Command%20or%20ANC%20was%20one%20to%20safeguard%20India%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20interests%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%2C%20by%20creating%20the%20potential%20for%20rapid%20multi-service%20deployment.%20The%20other%20was%20the%20Strategic%20Forces%20Command%20or%20SFC%2C%20tasked%20with%20the%20ownership%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20nuclear%20assets%2C%20deliverable%20by%20land-based%20mobile%20platforms%20and%20air%20and%20underwater%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Group%20of%20Ministers%20had%20reasoned%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20that%20being%20a%20mixed%20organisation%2C%20staffed%20by%20service%20and%20civilian%20personnel%2C%20HQ%20IDS%20would%20be%20able%20to%20integrate%20policies%20and%20doctrines%20of%20the%20individual%20services%20into%20joint%20documents%2C%20but%20little%20had%20since%20emerged%20or%20been%20achieved.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20IDS%20advanced%20its%20jointness%20agenda%20by%20promoting%20discourse%20on%20higher%20defence%20planning%20through%20the%20multi-service%20Centre%20for%20Joint%20Warfare%20Studies%20(CENJOWS)%20founded%20in%202007%20which%20too%20had%20proved%20disappointing%20as%20did%20three%20other%20service-specific%20think%20tanks%2C%20founded%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20(MoD).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20included%20the%20Centre%20for%20Air%20Power%20Studies%20or%20CAPS%20which%20came%20up%20in%202001%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Land%20Warfare%20Studies%20or%20CLAWS%2C%20created%20in%202004%2C%20while%20the%20National%20Maritime%20Foundation%20or%20NMF%20was%20the%20last%20to%20be%20inaugurated%2C%20in%202005.%20Additionally%2C%20the%2060-year-old%20MoD-financed%20Manohar%20Parrikar%20Institute%20for%20Defence%20Studies%20and%20Analyses%20(MP-IDSA)%20too%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20provided%20a%20workable%20proposal%20for%20higher%20defence%20reforms%2C%20let%20alone%20ITCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20several%20complex%20personnel%20and%20fiscal%20issues%20threaten%20the%20formation%20of%20ITCs%2C%20which%20have%20not%20received%20adequate%2C%20if%20any%2C%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20comprise%20the%20planned%20absorption%20into%20the%20ITCs%20of%20establishments%20like%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20and%20the%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20both%20managed%20presently%20by%20the%20MoD%20and%20Central%20Para%20Military%20Forces%20like%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%2C%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20the%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%2C%20which%20are%20run%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%20Integrating%20all%20these%20organisations%2C%20albeit%20partially%2C%20into%20the%20ITCs%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20without%20problems%2C%20as%20it%20will%20entail%20service%2C%20salary%20and%20retirement%20matters%20that%20invariably%20present%20grave%20obstacles%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20litigious%20environment%20that%20take%20years%20to%20resolve%20and%2C%20in%20many%20instances%2C%20end%20up%20being%20financially%20depleting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20more%20critical%20issue%20and%20one%20that%20dominates%20discussions%20within%20the%20services%20and%20the%20DMA%20is%20of%20parity%20in%20status%20and%20seniority%20of%20military%20officers%20presently%20heading%20the%2017%20existing%20single%20service%20geographical%20and%20functional%20commands.%20These%20comprise%20seven%20each%20for%20the%20army%20and%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20and%20three%20for%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20(IN)%2C%20all%20headed%20by%20a%20three-star%20officer.%20These%2017%20were%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20two%20tri-service%20commands%20mentioned%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20these%2017%20commands%20eventually%20being%20subsumed%20by%20three%2C%20four%20or%20even%20five%20ITCs%2C%20one%20immediate%20fallout%20will%20be%20the%20placation%20of%20around%2013-14%20three-star%20officers%2C%20who%20would%20be%20dispossessed%20of%20their%20elevated%20statuses.%20Additionally%2C%20some%2010-odd%20Principal%20Staff%20Officers%20(PSOs)%20at%20all%20three%20Services%20Headquarters%2C%20three%20vice%20chiefs%20and%20the%20IDS%20head%20would%20also%20need%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98adjusted%E2%80%99%20without%20losing%20their%20sheen%20and%20frills%20in%20the%20new%20ITC%20set-up%2C%20further%20engendering%20disaffection%20amongst%20senior%20military%20officers.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20numerous%20three-star%20Directorate%20heads%20at%20each%20service%20headquarters%20would%20also%20need%20to%20be%20similarly%20accommodated%20in%20this%20herculean%20ITC%20endeavour%2C%20albeit%20without%20rancour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERetired%20Lt%20General%20Raj%20Shukla%20who%20headed%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Training%20Command%20in%20Shimla%20declared%20at%20a%20recent%20seminar%20organised%20by%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20in%20Delhi%20in%20August%20that%20in%20the%20debate%20over%20the%20ITCs%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98services%20were%20behind%20the%20curve%E2%80%99.%20He%20also%20warned%20of%20%E2%80%98serious%20consequences%E2%80%99%20from%20China%20if%20India%20got%20this%20ITC%20concept%20wrong.%20Former%20IN%20Chief%20Admiral%20Arun%20Prakash%20concurred%2C%20declaring%20in%20the%20same%20discussion%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%98myopia%20and%20parochialism%E2%80%99%20within%20the%20armed%20forces%20over%20the%20ITCs%2C%20as%20the%20military%20was%20intrinsically%20opposed%20to%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20theatre%20command%20model%2C%20on%20which%20the%20Indian%20ITC%20template%20is%20largely%20believed%20to%20be%20patterned%2C%20the%20chain%20of%20military%20command%20flows%20from%20the%20president%20to%20the%20secretary%20of%20defence%20and%20onto%20the%20theatre%20commanders%20and%20back.%20The%20latter%20were%20overseen%20by%20another%20four-star%20chairman%20of%20the%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%20who%2C%20like%20India%E2%80%99s%20CDS%2C%20performed%20an%20advisory%20role%20to%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20political%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20nativised%2C%20this%20concept%20would%20incorporate%20ITC%20commanders%20reporting%20directly%20to%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20who%20then%2C%20like%20the%20US%20defence%20secretary%2C%20would%20be%20the%20deciding%20operational%20authority%2C%20but%20obviously%20with%20no%20military%20or%20battleground%20experience%2C%20like%20the%20majority%20of%20his%20predecessors.%20To%20overcome%20this%20handicap%2C%20a%20former%20IN%20chief%20had%20recently%20even%20suggested%20appointing%20a%20defence%20minister%20with%20intimate%20knowledge%20of%20military%20affairs%20with%20multi-party%20consensus.%20But%20such%20a%20fantasy%20remains%20just%20that%2C%20as%20such%20reasoning%20could%20be%20extended%20to%20include%20the%20appointment%20profile%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20entire%20federal%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02135655%2FF9XZ5mwbwAATvWn.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02135655%2FF9XZ5mwbwAATvWn.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02135655%2FF9XZ5mwbwAATvWn-300x159.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02135655%2FF9XZ5mwbwAATvWn-1024x542.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683133%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDefence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20with%20CDS%20Anil%20Chauhan%20and%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20V.R.%20Chaudhari.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40HQ_IDS_India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20the%20default%20option%20of%20revising%20the%20CDS%E2%80%99s%20charter%20and%20investing%20him%20with%20operational%20responsibility%20over%20the%20ITCs%20needed%20to%20be%20viewed%20with%20caution%2C%20warned%20Gen%20Hooda%20in%20his%20aforementioned%20analysis.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20political%20leadership%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20cautioned%20%E2%80%9Cmust%20decide%20on%20how%20much%20authority%20they%20wish%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20single%20(military)%20appointment.%E2%80%9D%20Such%20a%20decision%2C%20he%20added%2C%20would%20impact%20the%20nature%20of%20future%20civil-military%20relations%20and%20needed%20to%20be%20deliberated%20upon%20carefully.%20Gen%20Hooda%E2%80%99s%20caveat%20harks%20back%20to%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20when%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20arguments%20against%20appointing%20a%20CDS%20with%20operational%20authority%20was%20that%20it%20could%20have%20an%20%E2%80%98adverse%E2%80%99%20outcome%20that%20was%20analogous%20to%20%E2%80%98military%20upsets%E2%80%99%20that%20had%20occurred%20since%20Independence%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20other%20measures%20under%20consideration%20by%20the%20CDS%20that%20were%20delaying%20the%20ITCs%E2%80%99%20formal%20announcement%20reportedly%20included%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20vice%20CDS%20and%20deputy%20CDS%20to%20oversee%20assorted%20%E2%80%98verticals%E2%80%99%20in%20military%20planning%20like%20intelligence%20gathering%2C%20procurements%20and%20joint%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20the%20onus%20of%20concluding%20the%20ITC%20model%20in%20its%20fullness%2C%20especially%20its%20operational%20command%20and%20control%20framework%20is%20exclusively%20dependant%20on%20the%20DMA%20and%20the%20forces%20and%2C%20for%20a%20change%2C%20not%20on%20the%20political%20leadership%20which%20has%20green-lighted%20the%20entire%20ITC%20project%20and%20awaits%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20now%20up%20to%20the%20DMA%20and%20the%20CDS%20heading%20it%20to%20justify%20their%20averred%20inclusive%20military%20planning%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698916252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02135719%2FF92K5a0XsAAs1Bq.jpeg%22%2C%22origi